speech.p:
asked the Under-Secretary of State for Air (1) whether the order for compulsory purchase has been confirmed by

which the Darlington Corporation is to acquire for purposes of an aerodrome 370 acres on the south side of Yarn Road and east of Lingfield Lane; and what price has been fixed for this land;

(2) whether the order for compulsory purchase has been confirmed by which the Nottingham Corporation is to acquire approximately 166 acres at Tollerton for the purposes of an aerodrome; and what price has been fixed for this land?
